2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on downlink cellular networks, which are a type of wireless network. 
3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper deals with the spatial stochastic model of cellular networks, which can be considered as a type of social network. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) - The paper deals with the deployment of wireless base stations, which can be considered as agents in a multiagent system. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper may involve the use of algorithms and data structures to analyze the spatial stochastic model of cellular networks.
